inking I=E2=80=99ve got to find a way of
somehow getting into the inner sanctum to see this.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0

=C2=A0

But he didn=E2=80=99t want to ask Masa, lest he owe a debt to the subject o=
f his book. In the end, Masa brought it up himself at the end of an intervi=
ew. =E2=80=9CWe shook hands, and then he said, =E2=80=98I want to show you =
something,=E2=80=99=E2=80=9D Barber recalled. =E2=80=9CAnd he opened these =
doors, and there is this Xanadu meets Kyoto. There are three rock pools =E2=
=80=A6 and they=E2=80=99re
